🔷 STEP-WISE ALGORITHM FOR ipl points table System
Step 1: Start
Step 2: Declare variables for:
Team Name
Matches Played (M)
Wins (W)
Losses (L)
Points (P)
Step 3: Input the number of teams (n)
Step 4: Set i = 1
Step 5: Input the Team Name
Step 6: Input Matches Played (M)
Step 7: Input Wins (W)
Step 8: Calculate Losses
L = M − W
Step 9: Calculate Points
P = W × 2
Step 10: Store the team details
Step 11: Increase i = i + 1
Step 12: If i ≤ n, go to Step 5
Step 13: Sort teams in descending order of points
Step 14: Display the points table with ranking
Step 15: Stop
